SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c04236062
Version: 4

HPSBMU02994 rev.4 - HP BladeSystem c-Class Onboard Administrator (OA) running
OpenSSL, Remote Disclosure of Information

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as
soon as possible.

Release Date: 2014-04-13
Last Updated: 2014-05-06

Potential Security Impact: Remote disclosure of information

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
A potential security vulnerability has been identified in HP BladeSystem
c-Class Onboard Administrator (OA) running OpenSSL. This is the OpenSSL
vulnerability known as "Heartbleed" which could be exploited remotely
resulting in disclosure of information.

References: CVE-2014-0160, SSRT101500

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HP BladeSystem c-Class Onboard Administrator (OA) v4.11 and v4.20

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2014-0160    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:P/I:N/A:N)       5.0
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HP has made Onboard Administrator (OA) v4.12 and v4.21 available to resolve
the vulnerability here:

Go to:
http://www.hp.com/go/oa

Click "Onboard Administrator Firmware"
Select "HP BLc3000 Onboard Administrator Option" or "HP BLc7000 Onboard
Administrator Option"
Select an appropriate operating system from the list of choices
On the page, find Firmware 4.12 or v4.21 for download

Notes

No action is required unless the OA is running the firmware versions
explicitly listed as vulnerable.
HP CloudSystem Matrix 7.3 Update 1 v7.3.1.0 and HP CloudSystem built on
ConvergedSystem 700x solutions support customers moving from OA 4.11 to OA
4.12. Formal support documentation will be updated, see HPSBMU03028 HP Matrix
Operating Environment and CloudSystem Matrix, OpenSSL, CVE-2014-0160 here:
https://h20564.www2.hp.com/portal/site/hpsc/public/kb/docDisplay/?docId=emr_n
a-c04268239

